The paper presents a reinforcement learning technique that uses natural language as the goal representation to solve difficult 3D navigation tasks. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the sub-categories of Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), Machine Learning (cs.LG), Computational Linguistics (cs.CL), Robotics (cs.RO), and Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition (cs.CV).
